    Search the Catalogue Plus of the Württemberg State Library for books, journals, articles, maps, sheet music and other media from the following holdings and collections:
    <ul>
        <li>Württemberg State Library</li>
        <li>State Bibliography Baden-Württemberg</li>
        <li>International Hölderlin Bibliography</li>
        <li>Stefan George Bibliography</li>
        <li>German Central Pharmaceutical Library</li>
        <li>Academic libraries from the GBV and SWB network regions (K10plus)</li>
        <li>freely accessible online publications (Open Access)</li>
        <li>scientific articles from numerous databases</li>
    </ul>

    If you only want to search for holdings of the Württemberg State Library, limit the Advanced Search to "WLB holdings" or use the filter "WLB holdings" in your search results. For specific searches in the State Bibliography Baden-Württemberg and the bibliographies of the literary archives of Stefan George and Friedrich Hölderlin, you can also use the corresponding restriction in the Advanced Search or the filters in your search results. Media and individual articles that are not in the WLB collection can be ordered via the "Interlibrary Loan" tab.
